Uses of Package
com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute

  • Packages that use com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute 
    Package Description
    com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute
    The com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute package provides interfaces for quering the status of compute policies on virtual machines.
  • Classes in com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute used by com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute 
    Class and Description
    ComputeFactory
    ComputeFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vcenter.vm.compute package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    Policies
    The Policies interface provides methods to query the status of policies on virtual machines.
    PoliciesTypes
    The Policies interface provides methods to query the status of policies on virtual machines.
    PoliciesTypes.Info
    The Info class contains information about the compliance of a virtual machine with a compute policy.
